  "description": [
    "Page Six Soldiers Corner uuiHiiiiiiniNuuaiuiiuiiniiimMM AIR MEbAL AWARDED TO LT ROLAND NELSON MISSING IN ACTION The HeraldNews is in receipt this week of a note from Mr and Mrs Emil Nelson enclosing a let ter received by their sons wife Mrs Roland Nelson of Butte con cerning the Air Medal awarded to their son Lt Roland Nelson who has been missing in action since April 16th of this year No fur ther word has been received from the War Department as to his whereabouts up to the present time The letter from the War De partment telling of the award reads as follows Mrs Gertrude M Nelson 864 South Main Street Butte Montana Dear Mrs Nelson I have the honor to inform you that by direction of the Presi dent the Air Medal has been aw arded to your husband Second Lieutenant Roland F Nelson Air Corps The citation is as follows For meritorious achievement while participating from 3 Febru ary 1945 to 13 March 1945 in successful combat missions from a base in the Marianas Islands ag ainst the Japanese Empire All missions were flown without fight er escort under rapidly changing and ofttimes adverse weather conditions The flights"
